Additionally, the manufacturing sector utilizes half-cell potential testing for quality control and assurance purposes. From automotive to electronics manufacturing, ensuring the longevity and reliability of products is paramount. Half-cell potential tests enable manufacturers to detect early signs of corrosion in materials and components, thereby enhancing product durability and customer satisfaction.

